11:
A crude iron gunlance that,
despite its mass-produced
quality, packs quite a punch.
15:
A gunlance of fine steel, with
improved durability and power
for more demanding hunts.
19:
A lavish gunlance of rare steel
able to penetrate even the
hardest of shells with ease.
22:
The Nergigante scales on this
gunlance continually regrow,
promising unending pain to foes.
24:
Forged from Nergigante parts.
Its fangs bared, the sinner lost
in shadow at last sees light.
26:
The hank of white Tobi-Kadachi
fur wrapped around this gunlance
is forever charged with static.
30:
Each shot of the thunder-charged
Tobi-Kadachi gunlance seeks its
prey with a sickening roar.
34:
Residual heat in the Rathalos
parts used in this gunlance
grants it a searing strike.
37:
This vermilion gunlance is an
emblem of the Rathalos, and
shares its blazing roar.
39:
Each blast of this gunlance looses
the roar of the Azure Rathalos to
sear the sky and shake the earth.
42:
This Rathian gunlance's poisoned
prey turns the lush green of its
scales, while its shots draw red.
45:
Like the fury of a queen, this
Pink Rathian gunlance's ire is
quelled only by blood and flame.
48:
Fortified with Jyuratodus parts
and caked in mud, this gunlance
is as primal as it is deadly.
52:
Unrivaled in ferocity, a salvo
of shots from this Jyuratodus
gunlance will aerate anything.
56:
This icy, keenly honed Legiana
gunlance hums as it cuts
graceful arcs and figures.
59:
None can flee the spine-chilling
point of the Legiana gunlance,
scepter of the god of ice.
62:
A gunlance made from easily
obtainable bone. Rough-hewn, but
a sturdy friend to new hunters.
66:
Made from the densest of bones,
this gunlance offers more firepower
with the same ease of use.
70:
A gunlance made of modified bone.
The primal force of each shot can
bore through solid rock.
73:
A demonic Bazelgeuse gunlance
that scorches the earth with the
vast explosion each shot yields.
76:
Wrapped in supple Jagras hide,
this gunlance fits firmly in the
user's grip.
80:
Lavish use of butter-soft Jagras
hide makes this gunlance feel
like an extension of its user.
84:
Steeped in virulent Great Girros
toxin, this gunlance's bite
swiftly paralyzes its prey.
87:
The numbing sting of paralytic
toxin from this Great Girros
gunlance leaves prey defenseless.
91:
Drawing power from beyond death,
this Vaal Hazak gunlance serves
only those who embrace oblivion.
94:
Adding Barroth parts only made
this gunlance more stark and
brutish...in a good way.
98:
Imbued with the destructive
might of a Barroth, each shot
carves new scars into the earth.
102:
A gunlance wrapped in hide
tempered hard as iron in the
searing breath of an Anjanath.
105:
This Anjanath gunlance's point
burns all who come within its
reach to cinder.
109:
A dragon element gunlance
hewn from bone, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
114:
The hellish fury of this Zorah
gunlance erupts enough volcanic
power to halt a river's flow.
116:
A dragon element gunlance
forged in iron, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
119:
This Kushala Daora gunlance weds
the lion's imposing roar with
the biting talons of an eagle.
122:
A Xeno'jiiva gunlance, lord
among treasures. Its pitiless
judgment levels all before it.
124:
A Gunlance with the ravenous soul
of a Deviljho. Though twisted, the
beast's form is still apparent.
127:
A Kulve Taroth gunlance with
unknown traits. Its true potential
has yet to be realized.
131:
A Kulve Taroth gunlance that
utilizes other monster parts
for research purposes.
142:
A Kulve Taroth gunlance that
possesses new properties due to
clever material utilization.
153:
A Kulve Taroth gunlance that
fully harnesses the hidden power
of the materials used to create it.
157:
A hidden power seeps from
this Lunastra gunlance, as
if a soul is trapped inside.
159:
This Lunastra gunlance was
forged in hellfire. Sometimes
guards its user from fatal blows.
161:
This Lunastra gunlance resonates
with the added Nergigante parts
to give a chance for regeneration.
163:
This Lunastra gunlance resonates
with the added Xeno'jiiva parts
to help keep your weapon sharp.
166:
A unique gunlance made from the
gold of Kulve Taroth. Houses the
true might of the goddess within.
174:
Crafted specifically for the Defense
Corps, its high-performance
output is thanks to modern tech.
190:
Using only the rarest of metals,
this gunlance can blast through
even the toughest defense.
194:
This gunlance is so sharp,
it's almost as if the spirit of
a Yian Garuga possesses it.
197:
Do not avert thy wicked eyes.
This Ruiner Nergigante gunlance
breathes the fires of perdition.
201:
The twin points of this elegant
Viper Tobi-Kadachi gunlance
hold terrible destructive power.
207:
Made from Silver Rathalos parts,
the argent scales on the body of
this gunlance emit a noble shine.
211:
A Gold Rathian gunlance.
Its fragile beauty is the
last thing foes ever see.
213:
This Jyuratodus gunlance
boasts overwhelming power,
derived from humble mud.
216:
The icy fangs of this Barioth
gunlance saps the warmth
from its prey with each bite.
221:
Rumble like thunder, and let the
snowy tip of Shrieking Legiana's
talon freeze all it touches.
223:
The Nargacuga parts used in this
gunlance are sharp enough to cut
you just by looking at them.
226:
A gunlance made of only
the rarest bones. Powerful
enough to blast apart steel.
230:
The icy point of this Velkhana
gunlance freezes the final cries
of its prey in their throat.
233:
All life trembles before the
howls produced by this Seething
Bazelgeuse gunlance.
235:
The bold fur upon this Banbaro
gunlance sends a challenge to
any brave enough to take it.
240:
A Zinogre gunlance.
Its mighty roar heralds the
coming of the world conqueror.
244:
A flawless gunlance modeled after
a Stygian Zinogre. The shells it
fires portend the end of the world.
247:
This Great Jagras gunlance
handles so easily it feels like
an extension of one's arm.
250:
A gunlance made from Tigrex
materials. Its roar sends
wyverns running for roost.
254:
Caution is needed when wielding
this Great Girros gunlance, for it
contains a potent paralytic toxin.
257:
This Glavenus gunlance stokes
the flame of a hunter's passion
to sear all who dare oppose.
262:
The fallen revel at every thrust
of this unerring Blackveil Vaal
Hazak gunlance.
264:
The acid flowing from the tip of
this Acidic Glavenus gunlance
weakens its prey from within.
267:
Stout and unyielding, this
Barroth gunlance bores
the earth with each thrust.
270:
Brachydios's distinct explosive
slime coats this gunlance,
blasting the foes it pierces.
273:
A gunlance whose every blast of light
harnesses Raging Brachydios's rage
as it rocks heaven's foundation.
275:
The undying flame within this
Anjanath gunlance will see all
in its reach burned to ash.
278:
An untamed Fulgur Anjanath 
gunlance that barely contains
the furious lightning within it.
281:
A dragon element gunlance
hewn from bone, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
284:
The earth's fury roars forth as
this Shara Ishvalda gunlance
brings release to the tainted.
287:
Endless darkness dances on the
blade of this Namielle gunlance,
guiding prey into the abyss.
292:
A Savage Deviljho gunlance.
One blast frees its mighty
impulse from its chains.
294:
This Rajang gunlance may look
generic at first glance, but each
part contains a demonic force.
296:
The unbridled anger contained in
this Furious Rajang gunlance serves
to unleash devastating blasts.
298:
At the epicenter of a great war,
this Alatreon gunlance was found,
pierced in the ground.
304:
A gunlance made from Brute
Tigrex materials. Its roar sends
wyverns running for roost.
307:
A fusion of Gajalaka culture and
Smithy tech, packed with high
explosives. Not for the timid.
310:
Bestowed upon guild knights with
stellar achievements. The sublime
glow is a source of pride.
319:
A silver Frostfang Barioth gunlance
enveloped by a sharp cold.
Proof of the hoarfrost's keeper.
321:
A Fatalis gunlance that
curses with its evil gaze.
Its very glimmer instills fear.
331:
A gunlance made from Safi'jiiva
parts. Awaken its hidden potential
by using unique materials.
